@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@findingId = 请替换为finding_id
@chatSessionId = 请替换为session_id

### 健康检查
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### JSON 条款导入
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contracts/imports/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contract_no": "CG-HTTP-001",
  "name": "HTTP 示例采购合同",
  "contract_type_code": "PURCHASE",
  "counterparty": "示例供应商",
  "amount": 100000,
  "currency": "CNY",
  "clauses": [
    {
      "clause_no": "第一条",
      "title": "付款方式",
      "content": "验收合格后十个工作日内付款。"
    },
    {
      "clause_no": "第二条",
      "title": "交付方式",
      "content": "供应方应在约定日期前完成交付。"
    }
  ]
}

### TXT 文件解析预览（不会写数据库）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contracts/imports/preview/file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="contract_no"

CG-HTTP-002
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

TXT 示例采购合同
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="contract_type_code"

PURCHASE
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="contract-import.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./examples/contract-import.txt
--WebAppBoundary--

### 确认 TXT 解析结果并正式入库
# 把上一个请求返回的 preview_hash 填入下面字段。
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contracts/imports/confirm/file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="preview_hash"

请替换为预览接口返回的preview_hash
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="payload"
Content-Type: application/json

< ./examples/contract-import.json
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="contract-import.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./examples/contract-import.txt
--WebAppBoundary--

### 查询向量化进度
# 把 document_id 替换为确认导入接口返回的值。
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contracts/imports/请替换为document_id/vectorization
Accept: application/json

### JSON 制度依据导入
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/policies/imports/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policy_no": "ZD-HTTP-001",
  "title": "采购合同管理制度",
  "version": "V1.0",
  "issuer": "采购管理部",
  "effective_date": "2026-07-01",
  "sections": [
    {
      "section_no": "第三条",
      "title": "预付款控制",
      "content": "采购合同预付款比例原则上不得超过合同总价的百分之三十。"
    },
    {
      "section_no": "第九条",
      "title": "质量保证",
      "content": "一般办公设备的质保期原则上不得少于十二个月。"
    }
  ]
}

### TXT 制度文件解析预览（不会写数据库）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/policies/imports/preview/file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=PolicyBoundary

--PolicyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="policy_no"

ZD-HTTP-002
--PolicyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

采购合同管理制度
--PolicyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="version"

V1.0
--PolicyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="demo-procurement-policy.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./output/txt/demo-procurement-policy.txt
--PolicyBoundary--

### 查询制度向量化进度
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/policies/imports/请替换为document_id/vectorization
Accept: application/json

### 查询可审查合同
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/risk-reviews/contracts
Accept: application/json

### 创建付款、质保、违约责任和争议解决四分支并行风险审查
# contract_id 来自合同导入响应；合同和制度需先完成向量化。
# 合同侧向量 Top 3；制度侧向量 Top 10，经重排序后取 Top 5。
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/risk-reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contract_id": "请替换为contract_id"
}

### 查询审查进度及证据报告
# review_run_id 来自创建风险审查响应。
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/risk-reviews/请替换为review_run_id
Accept: application/json

### 为风险项创建或恢复多轮问答会话
# finding_id 来自风险审查详情中某一项 finding；会话会固定该风险项、审查任务和合同修订版本。
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/risk-findings/{{findingId}}/chat-sessions
Accept: application/json

### 查询会话历史、结构化草案和可追溯引用
# 把创建或恢复会话响应中的 session_id 填入顶部 chatSessionId 变量。
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}
Accept: application/json

### 解释已有风险结论
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "为什么这一项被判断为高风险？",
  "intent": "EXPLAIN",
  "client_request_id": "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111111"
}

### 查询合同条款与制度依据
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "请列出支持这项结论的合同条款和制度依据。",
  "intent": "EVIDENCE_QUERY",
  "client_request_id": "22222222-2222-4222-8222-222222222222"
}

### 根据风险建议生成条款修改草案
# 草案只保存在助手消息中，不会写回合同，也不会自动影响审批。
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "请在保留百分之二十预付款的前提下生成修改草案。",
  "intent": "DRAFT_CLAUSE",
  "client_request_id": "33333333-3333-4333-8333-333333333333"
}

### 自由追问并由后端自动判断意图
# intent 可省略，后端默认使用 AUTO；同一 client_request_id 重试时请求内容必须保持一致。
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "上一版草案为什么这样调整？",
  "client_request_id": "44444444-4444-4444-8444-444444444444"
}

### 查询辅助审批候选报告
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/approvals/candidates
Accept: application/json

### 创建固定业务、法务两级审批
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/approvals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "review_run_id": "请替换为review_run_id"
}

### 查询审批详情
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/approvals/请替换为approval_instance_id
Accept: application/json

### 处理当前审批节点
# 退回 RETURNED 或驳回 REJECTED 时 comment 必填。
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/approvals/请替换为approval_instance_id/actions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approver_name": "演示审批人",
  "decision": "APPROVED",
  "comment": "已核对风险依据，同意进入下一节点。"
}
